bodyArticleHtml:
2002-07-17

know what sux?

diesel.2y.net no longer exists, everything that was once on diesel.2y.net is now diesel.ath.cx. dhs.org owns 2y.net, and they want a $5 donation in order to keep the domain names up for a year. F that.
